dct_title_s: South America, Brazil--south coast, Baía da Ilha Grande including Baía da Ribeira and Baía de Jacuacanga (Raster Image)
dct_description_sm: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours, hachures, and spot heights. "From Brazilian and U.S. charts to 1990." "Copyright restrictions of the country of origin continue to exist." "Soundings in meters." Includes source diagram and tidal information. Map no.24153
This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
